~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : listbans                                  ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : listbans sites/users/swears

   This will list all the sites or all the users currently banned from
   logging in. Also it can list the currently banned swear words.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ban, unban
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

